{"nodes":[{"id":"97d34fa2-6028-407f-b5db-0bc8ceb4d4f9","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Создание персонажа","content":{"items":[{"id":"37a146a0-1bf9-4898-8f89-efe0ac3c0fc9","type":"text","text":"*Все похождения начинаются с хорошо запоминающегося имени! Кто ты?*","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"70f9e370-a046-4b7c-b7a5-82d60036d0d3","type":"input","text":"Имя","targetNodeId":"8b90b0ea-e14a-4ba6-8b31-1122c92130c2","variableName":"Имя","placeholderText":"На русском, только буквы","buttonText":"Подтвердить","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":180.0,"y":400.0,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"8b90b0ea-e14a-4ba6-8b31-1122c92130c2","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Раса","content":{"items":[{"id":"7ce11551-ab19-4cc2-a7e2-d70d731a5386","type":"text","text":"*Откуда ты родом, из какого народа?*","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"225b0aa1-3c29-4318-a041-688ca174c5c3","type":"text","text":"","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ff743323-8c04-470a-8c07-f5c2edc4e34e","type":"column","children":[{"id":"419d6de3-c881-4c84-be22-aad257c8367f","type":"text","text":"**Человек**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"116bf59c-b5f7-4285-bb68-12f49e26b5cb","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/fb91b685-79fd-46b1-8251-fda035002836.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8088df1d-71c9-4e43-9c0d-79c85a57346b","type":"text","text":"> Ничем не выдающийся народ, однако люди всегда стрямятся к чему-то новому!\n\n- Множитель опыта: 2x","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"60c5e244-db2b-4eb1-afc9-39373b6965bc","type":"button","text":"*Человек*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/7e7380b9-00ed-40e4-bed0-a3c8296d96fb.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ed186a79-2591-4bb8-95bc-f3381c7065a8","type":"text","text":"","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"89bd548f-0465-4727-97cc-03f67b55f2fc","type":"column","children":[{"id":"e4040b86-6a59-42b9-9527-cfbd776423d4","type":"text","text":"**Орк**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3c114789-a9f8-4232-9232-fee57a7c2189","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/c8e8670e-ac96-4fce-b03a-27018211c965.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ebdb5597-8ea5-4a82-b72e-6f0dfcf314b0","type":"text","text":"> Воинственная зеленокожая раса, немного туповаты и не дипломатичны, но зато у них хорошая мускулатура\n\n- +5 к Силе\n- -5 к Интеллекту\n- +5 к Телу\n- -5 к Общению","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"fbb0e768-0e83-4918-b48d-5e8f018ff61b","type":"button","text":"*Орк*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/b6ed883c-a6a2-481b-866d-38114b2adf99.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"333b3cc1-5f67-4738-96c7-ef2469c465a4","type":"text","text":"","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"bc838be1-032d-4438-91e8-3447494409b4","type":"column","children":[{"id":"7ca4808a-585c-493a-b8e9-b45606832de0","type":"text","text":"**Кондр**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"96839a33-3d22-4446-9aec-528908048ab7","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/ce10969d-d460-490c-9bf3-2a965acc80a0.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"bb3b98e4-572c-443d-bbfb-408dc7d50551","type":"text","text":"> Ловкие и хитрые потомки людей— отличные воры, убийцы и мошенники, однако они достаточно слабы и хрупки, поэтому старайтесь не нагружать себя **Тяжёлой** бронёй во избежание штрафов\n\n- +5 к Проворству\n- +5 к Ловкости рук\n- -5 к Телу\n- -5 к Силе","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ec464e2d-1665-4c59-97bd-19bba9937a80","type":"button","text":"*Кондр*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/a34e6a89-fa3b-4921-84f5-0a4ee6f235c8.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"9c50f58a-6ecb-47a9-b463-2911f9403637","type":"text","text":"","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"60b25b7e-efb9-441e-871e-fd4866265619","type":"column","children":[{"id":"5f2a719d-6220-4e3e-b4ec-21edf59ad83a","type":"text","text":"**Импир**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1dae18e3-4a25-43fc-9b6e-c23fac3cfb50","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/8f70719b-d819-4396-a0ef-ac27b32c6681.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"28df595b-d9e2-46d1-80e6-e517c56559bc","type":"text","text":"> Производное от \"Империя\" и \"вампир\". Дипломатичны, но им важна только выгода и деньги, а также они плохо себя чувствуют на солнце\n\n- -5 к Мудрости\n- +5 к Общению","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6c894cc4-98c3-4796-9806-dca8a12adb01","type":"button","text":"*Импир*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/37a101d6-757e-4edc-a74a-a2f95a615e4f.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":513.5,"y":405.5,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"c2fbadcd-19cf-4574-b874-12354de5bfef","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Класс","content":{"items":[{"id":"fc0f7292-8337-407d-873b-76eaa5e6d105","type":"text","text":"*{Раса}, значит, хороший выбор...*\n*Но ведь иметь свое призвание в мире— еще лучше, да?*","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6882d2fc-626e-4bdb-8dad-236300aad0c4","type":"column","children":[{"id":"80d1d579-0ce9-4e54-b1f9-de91bc25b435","type":"text","text":"**Воин**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"515020f3-f8ed-45e6-956e-4f3ceeba2851","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/9c0df75b-0332-4755-ad07-73681d46c22f.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b782a58f-444c-453b-9ffa-80450546f0b0","type":"text","text":"> Классика, но многозначная. Наемник? Паладин? Варвар? Список можно продолжать бесконечно...\n\nНавыки:\n- Топоры\n- Дубины\n- Секиры\n- Копья\n- Мечи\n- Уклонение\n- Стойкость\n- Парирование","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d464555c-f8e7-402d-af25-a3c674f0c2ec","type":"button","text":"*Воин*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/c7aeff61-1229-4d60-8aa6-1cbc1d6056d6.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b7453534-ca9e-4619-9e62-5552e370af52","type":"column","children":[{"id":"ac952fe5-b395-4e17-b691-009c909223a6","type":"text","text":"**Пройдоха**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"638ef2e8-9095-4998-acb3-783457b16a1e","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/bc94d53c-669d-4e88-9a2b-c6873ee19ef8.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8bc4307a-5cf7-4b7b-8f57-7aec45c15cde","type":"text","text":"> Не самый лучший вариант для открытого боя, но если вы любите уворачиваться от ударов и красть что-то, то вам точно понравится\n\nНавыки:\n- Взлом\n- Мечи\n- Кинжалы\n- Уклонение\n- Убийство / оглушение со спины\n- Воровство\n- Скрытность","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"72661898-0df8-4523-aa1e-0d0fe5b314f7","type":"button","text":"*Пройдоха*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/97624234-d9c6-4e00-b13d-4e48cd0d099e.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"06b611a9-146f-4e44-b032-255d4cc17943","type":"column","children":[{"id":"82727891-f3b5-4e1b-b9b4-ae8f203cfb4d","type":"text","text":"**Работяга**","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f8809994-481e-49a2-bddd-086991cc1344","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/aab752e7-fdb7-4029-a66a-fd8d69f71d9c.jpg","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"238b3301-0299-4574-9e34-5d137bfbdf79","type":"text","text":"> То есть, ты не хочешь идти на работу в реальности, но хочешь работать в игровой кузнице? Короче, работяги отличные ремесленники, лесорубы, фермеры, повара, и шахтеры. Не предназначено для боев!\n\nНавыки:\n- Кузнечное дело\n- Дубильное дело\n- Шахтерское дело\n- Молоты\n- Топоры\n- Лесорубное дело\n- Фермерское дело","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"be72708a-686e-4c8c-97a8-d4388fbc1ede","type":"button","text":"*Работяга*","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/90adb45d-a03f-479e-bb7d-7e0bcc4f0f30.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}],"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":768.0,"y":401.0,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"ef199ecc-eca0-4522-8aca-e94cc8670911","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Тренировочный бой","content":{"items":[{"id":"e8ac4119-f578-4ba3-b509-a7ccbc2bced9","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/5b8e815d-4dad-4476-beb2-02be1542465a.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"036128d4-398f-43a6-b010-88ccc65e059f","type":"text","text":"—Я вижу, ты совсем новичок в плане боя...","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"941fcc29-d501-4b1b-bf7c-c5ea3a4def4b","type":"button","text":"—Научите меня, пожалуйста","targetNodeId":"2f82eba8-813f-4832-a0d2-a3397f7fb0cc","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a340621b-7568-4e7c-9bb9-7a8ab010db81","type":"button","text":"—Да я сегодня просто плохо спал, вот и оружие из рук падает (*Пропустить обучение*)","targetNodeId":"635496fd-708a-4652-a6e9-1dbaa05b7574","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":1013.0,"y":395.5,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"2f82eba8-813f-4832-a0d2-a3397f7fb0cc","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Быстро, но слабо","content":{"items":[{"id":"e4e07986-4ff5-4a8e-b0cd-6b5207687745","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/5b8e815d-4dad-4476-beb2-02be1542465a.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d8f23331-0ce0-4c65-a5e0-4a0b0759f93a","type":"text","text":"—Начнем с простого. Ударь меня","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e14468bd-19ae-4c0f-87c7-f1e4109f35aa","type":"text","text":"> *Нажмите [**Быстрая атака**], чтобы выполнить быстрый, но слабый удар*","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"f083788f-8cf1-4f48-840e-7ebf6354b7f9","type":"button","text":"***Быстрая атака***","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/f9bec4e5-cc1d-413c-835d-9f0dd5064bc7.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":1468.5546101677057,"y":570.0169554772818,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"color":4280492835},{"id":"a32ef7b4-6cbb-487b-ba02-fa06ff0352f1","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Тренировка парирования","content":{"items":[{"id":"26198536-c6f4-4559-8f25-74072ef80f51","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/5b8e815d-4dad-4476-beb2-02be1542465a.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"852c7699-d2ce-442d-a771-f3c87abf9b5b","type":"text","text":"—Ладно, теперь попробуй заблокировать мой удар!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3d143368-3b08-45cb-9e29-ce0be67d16e2","type":"button","text":"***Парирование***","targetNodeId":"494eb518-ef6a-41f8-991b-7dee9f329ce5","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":1757.0705446261252,"y":361.7225247463351,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0,"defaultActionNodeId":"ef199ecc-eca0-4522-8aca-e94cc8670911","timerDuration":3.0},{"id":"b72d23fa-4f9f-4897-a8e3-ad4b73bbe375","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Долго, но мощно!","content":{"items":[{"id":"68d2d074-9b0d-4d36-b104-d3c04d924096","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/5b8e815d-4dad-4476-beb2-02be1542465a.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"07692276-1d91-47fc-a77c-b449ed275785","type":"text","text":"—Иногда, когда сила важнее скорости, надо использовать **заряженные** атаки","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c44bb597-5784-44ae-bfcf-668cb8f73395","type":"button","text":"**Заряженная атака**","targetNodeId":"512ffa69-4ff7-41d3-8512-5c354c205842","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":2862.5050435904486,"y":352.3690594325597,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"494eb518-ef6a-41f8-991b-7dee9f329ce5","chapterId":"f730f1f1-3507-4223-acbc-653e2ba06acb","title":"Ай!","content":{"items":[{"id":"0bf9fbe4-6424-48b4-af46-add064640c21","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/5b8e815d-4dad-4476-beb2-02be1542465a.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"2a9d198c-fd1f-4cd3-bf19-5fce2b5e9904","type":"text","text":"—Ладно, но вот этот удар невозможно заблокировать!","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b073b370-1cf5-4cb6-a0c7-7da443826cf7","type":"button","text":"***Парировать***","scriptTriggers":{"onPress":"scripts/28244194-7958-4708-a690-94fb672c40b3.json"},"flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e8ca6a7e-d131-4ef4-b843-6de56ba795b7","type":"script","resourcePath":"scripts/a87d5451-eb09-42e5-97